  "subject": "Enhance helm plugin to allow parallel chart deployment",
  "commit_message": "Enhance helm plugin to allow parallel chart deployment\n\n- add --parallel and --parallel-max <N> flags to helm deploy plugin\n  that run the helm deploy in parallel\n- this enhances the plugin which currently deploys sequentially in\n  alphabetical order\n- change SDNC's readiness probe to a health endpoint instead of a socket [0]\n\n[0] this makes sure that the app only receives traffic when it is really ready.\n    also this will delay the tests of the gating pipeline and makes sure that\n    they only run when all apps are ready\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-3390\nChange-Id: I70876fc049ebcfb6d465a441ae6fb0060f71cd72\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
